---
title: Chicken Breast and Falafel Platters with Roasted Potatoes and Garlic Hummus Drizzle
description: Falafel doesn't have to be confined to a pita! Tonight's dinner takes an ordinary falafel and transforms it into something special. Be prepared for your plate to be stuffed to the brim with chicken breast, crispy roasted potatoes, garlic hummus and red peppers!
